                "code": "-- Setting time to 3 minutes causes mission to end\ngameTimeLimit:setTime(180000)\n\n-- Pop all menu screens\nwhile #menuStack > 0 do\n  table.remove(menuStack)\n  table.remove(inputStack)\nend\n\n-- Set message that player has quit\nendingMessage:setValue(\"Cartographer Quit: Mission Aborted\")\n\n-- Get rid of the prompt\nscreen:setScreen(nil)\n\n-- Unpause the game\nlocks = locks - 1\nif locks == 0 then\n  spindizzy:setPause(false)\n  if GlobalExplorer ~= 1 then\n    gameTimeLimit:play()\n  end\nend\n\n-- Disable menu access\nhasFocus = false"
